}

@*
    A template rendering a method/constructor/indexer/operator/delegate method parameter.

    This component is intended to be displayed in the 'Parameters' section within the declaration of a member.
    Optionally, it is possible to reuse this component in 'MethodDeclaration', 'ConstructorDeclaration', 'IndexerDeclaration',
    'OperatorDeclaration' and 'DelegateMethod' components to render the individual parameters.
*@
